products.name: Avengers: Endgame
products.description: After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War (2018), the universe is in ruins. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers assemble once more in order to reverse Thanos actions and restore balance to the universe.

products.name: Black Widow
products.description: A film about Natasha Romanoff in her quests between the films Civil War and Infinity War

products.name: Spider-Man: Far from Home
products.description: Following the events of Avengers: Endgame (2019), Spider-Man must step up to take on new threats in a world that has changed forever.

products.name: Captain Marvel
products.description: Carol Danvers becomes one of the universe"s most powerful heroes when Earth is caught in the middle of a galactic war between two alien races.

products.name: Avengers: Infinity War
products.description: The Avengers and their allies must be willing to sacrifice all in an attempt to defeat the powerful Thanos before his blitz of devastation and ruin puts an end to the universe.
